"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?11/22/11626?source=see_link\">",
"      Initial treatment of dermatomyositis and polymyositis in adults",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?24/7/24697?source=see_link\">",
