"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?8/7/8313?source=see_link\">",
"      Interstitial lung disease in dermatomyositis and polymyositis: Treatment",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?37/42/38566?source=see_link\">",
"      Malignancy in dermatomyositis and polymyositis",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?28/43/29368?source=see_link\">",
