"   <h1>",
"    REFERENCES",
"   </h1>",
"   <ol id=\"reference\">",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"UTD.htm?26/11/26810/abstract/1\">",
"      Sekhon LH, Fehlings MG. Epidemiology, demographics, and pathophysiology of acute spinal cord injury. Spine (Phila Pa 1976) 2001; 26:S2.",
"     </a>",
